                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-555-18600611 t18600611-555-punishment-42"></join>Four Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">There was another indictment against the prisoner.</hi>
